<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>count the cost • count the pennies</xh5><p> <i>count the cost—</i>estimate the advantages and disadvantages of an undertaking: Riding out, they didn’t <u>count the cost</u>; they had one end in view—to serve their king.</p><p> <i>count the pennies</i>—(also: count pennies) calculate costs carefully; be economical: That [dinner] was very expensive too. I wasn’t in the mood to <u>count the pennies</u>.</p> </entry>
